title: Up Then It's Stuck - Featuring Kia Miakka Natisse of NPR's Invisibilia
itunes:author: Loud Speakers Network
itunes:summary:
On this week’s episode of #TheFriendZone, we’re joined by Kia Miakka Natisse - co-host of NPR’s Invisibilia podcast. We discuss having deep faith in every chapter of your winding road, even when it feels like you can’t see where you’re going.
